<br>
IMO, they need to raise the wizzy spell rank on the 58 pets to include level 24 spells (including the Ice nuke -- why not, its a wizard, not a &quot;fire&quot; elem anymore..), and the rank on the 63 one to use level 29 spells (like thunderstrike and inferno shock).<br>
<br>
On top of all that, they need to restore the dmg shield, for sheer roleplay reasons.  The thing looks to be made of freakin' lava, after all, and it would be the ONLY part, besides the innate resists, that really had anything to do with the element of Fire (at the moment they are just weak wizzies, not &quot;fire elementals&quot;).  The fire pets have low hp anyway -- no reason they can't have a worthwhile damage shield.<br>
